<p style="font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; color: #444444; font-size: 14px;">&ldquo;<em>My job is specifically focused on how we get products from the bench to the clinic, and doing that in a much faster way,&rdquo; Tong said. &ldquo;Because of the work we&rsquo;ve done in the HIV vaccine space, we&rsquo;re really set up nicely to pivot to do this type of work.&rdquo; </em>- Tina Tong, DrPH student</p>
