<li style="font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: #444444; font-size: 14px;">You can access the University Calendar here: <a style="color: #41b6e6;" href="https://catalog.uic.edu/ucat/academic-calendar/#Fall2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #41b6e6;">UIC Academic Calendar</span></a></li>
